The first step in increasing advertising scale is (1) making the advertisin=
g tier more attractive, which Netflix did by improving the product experien=
ce to the =E2=80=9Cstandard=E2=80=9D level, and (2) increasing the delta be=
tween the advertising tier and the non-advertising tier, thus capturing mor=
e price-sensitive customers. This is what happened last week.

